OL,3,CNurse jailed for murder of elderly
OL,4,Cpatients in Leeds loses conviction
OL,5,Cappeals
OL,7,FNurse Colin Campbell, formerly known
OL,8,Fas Colin Norris, who was jailed for
OL,9,Flife in 2008 for the murders of four
OL,10,Felderly patients and attempting to
OL,11,Fmurder a fifth, has lost appeals
OL,12,Fagainst his convictions at the Court
OL,13,Fof Appeal.
OL,15,FHe was found guilty in 2008 of killing
OL,16,FDoris Ludlam, Bridget Bourke, Irene
OL,17,FCrookes and Ethel Hall.
