OL,4,Cpatients in Leeds loses conviction
OL,5,Cappeals
OL,7,FIn a 14-day hearing earlier this year,
OL,8,FMr Campbell's lawyers argued that new
OL,9,Fexpert knowledge meant the convictions
OL,10,Fwere now unsafe while lawyers for the
OL,11,FCrown Prosecution Service said much of
OL,12,Fthe same evidence presented was heard
OL,13,Fby the jury at trial.
OL,15,FIn a ruling on Thursday, 26 June,
OL,16,Fjudges dismissed his appeals.
