OL,7,FIn their judgment, Lady Justice Macur,
OL,8,FMr Justice Picken and Sir Stephen
OL,9,FIrwin, said: "We have no doubt about
OL,10,Fthe safety of any of the five
OL,11,Fconvictions. The appeals are
OL,12,Fdismissed."
